---
// Real MLogTech live tracking map (replaces the earlier stylized SVG).
// Below the fold on the home live-tracking section, so it loads lazily.
---

<figure
  class="overflow-hidden rounded-[var(--r-lg)] border border-hair bg-surface shadow-[var(--shadow-md)]"
>
  <img
    src="/images/product/panel-tracking.jpg"
    alt="MLogTech live tracking map: a driver's route across the region with delivery progress at 46 of 46 parcels"
    width="1500"
    height="782"
    loading="lazy"
    class="block w-full"
  />
</figure>
